### 2.3 Typography

#### **Font Family**

```css
--font-sans: "Inter", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
--font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
```

**Font Weights:**

- Regular: 400 (body text)
- Medium: 500 (labels, UI elements)
- Semibold: 600 (headings, emphasis)
- Bold: 700 (only for marketing, not in app)

#### **Type Scale**

```css
/* Headings */
--text-6xl: 60px / 72px (60/1.2) /* Hero - marketing only */
--text-5xl: 48px / 60px (48/1.25) /* H1 - page titles */
--text-4xl: 36px / 44px (36/1.22) /* H2 - section titles */
--text-3xl: 30px / 36px (30/1.2) /* H3 - card titles */
--text-2xl: 24px / 32px (24/1.33) /* H4 - subsections */
--text-xl:  20px / 28px (20/1.4) /* H5 - small headings */

/* Body */
--text-lg:   18px / 28px (18/1.56) /* Large body */
--text-base: 16px / 24px (16/1.5) /* Default body */
--text-sm:   14px / 20px (14/1.43) /* Small text, labels */
--text-xs:   12px / 16px (12/1.33) /* Captions, metadata */
```

#### **Usage Guidelines**

- **Page titles:** text-5xl (48px) semibold
- **Section headings:** text-2xl (24px) semibold
- **Card titles:** text-lg (18px) semibold
- **Body text:** text-base (16px) regular
- **Form labels:** text-sm (14px) medium
- **Helper text:** text-sm (14px) regular, slate-600
- **Metadata:** text-xs (12px) regular, slate-500

