## 3. Component Library

### 3.1 Buttons

#### **Primary Button**

```tsx
<button
  className="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2
  px-4 py-2 
  text-sm font-medium text-white
  bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700
  rounded-md
  shadow-sm
  transition-colors duration-200
  focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2
  disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed
"
>
  <Icon className="w-4 h-4" />
  Button Text
</button>
```

**Variants:**

- **Primary:** Blue background, white text (main actions)
- **Secondary:** White background, slate border, slate text (secondary actions)
- **Destructive:** Red background, white text (delete, reject)
- **Ghost:** Transparent background, slate text (tertiary actions)
- **Link:** No background, blue text, underline on hover

**Sizes:**

- **Small:** px-3 py-1.5 text-xs (32px height)
- **Default:** px-4 py-2 text-sm (40px height)
- **Large:** px-6 py-3 text-base (48px height)

#### **Button States**

- **Default:** Primary color
- **Hover:** Darker shade, slight shadow
- **Active:** Pressed effect, scale(0.98)
- **Focus:** Ring outline (accessibility)
- **Disabled:** 50% opacity, cursor-not-allowed
- **Loading:** Spinner icon, disabled state

