Overall = (Quality * 0.3) + (Delivery * 0.3) + (Service * 0.2) + (Cost * 0.2)

Finalize:
├── Validation: All required fields
├── Confirmation modal
├── Locks evaluation (no further edits)
└── Sends notifications
```

