## 6. User Flows

### 6.1 Complete Supplier Qualification Flow

```mermaid
Start
  ↓
Add Supplier (basic info)
  ↓
Supplier Detail Page
  ↓
Click "Start Qualification"
  ↓
[Modal] Confirm qualification details
  ↓
Qualification Questionnaire (Stage 1)
  ├→ Answer questions (15)
  ├→ Upload documents (3-5 required)
  ├→ View risk score (auto-calculated)
  └→ Save as draft OR Submit
  ↓
[Notification] Procurement Manager receives email
  ↓
Procurement Review (Stage 2)
  ├→ Review all answers
  ├→ Review documents
  ├→ Add notes
  └→ Decision:
      ├→ Request Changes → Back to Stage 1
      ├→ Reject → Supplier status = Blocked
      └→ Approve → Continue
  ↓
[Notification] Quality Manager receives email
  ↓
Quality/Management Approval (Stage 3)
  ├→ Final review
  ├→ Add final notes
  └→ Decision:
      ├→ Reject → Supplier status = Blocked
      └→ Approve → Supplier status = Qualified
  ↓
[Notification] All stakeholders notified
  ↓
Supplier Status Updated
  ↓
End
```

**Key UI Touchpoints:**

1. Supplier List → Add New Supplier button
2. Supplier Detail → Start Qualification button
3. Qualification Form → Progress bar, collapsible sections
4. Review Pages → Read-only view, action buttons
5. Email Notifications → Links back to qualification

**Error Paths:**

- Incomplete questionnaire → Cannot submit
- Missing required documents → Validation error
- Network error → Toast notification, auto-retry

---

### 6.2 Register and Resolve Complaint Flow

```mermaid
Start
  ↓
Discover Issue
  ↓
Navigate: Complaints → New Complaint
  ↓
Register Complaint Form
  ├→ Select supplier
  ├→ Choose category, severity
  ├→ Describe problem
  ├→ Upload photos/documents
  ├→ Assign to user
  └→ Submit
  ↓
Complaint Created (Status: Open)
  ↓
[Notification] Assigned user + supplier contact
  ↓
Complaint Detail Page
  ↓
Investigation Phase
  ├→ Add internal notes
  ├→ Change status to "Investigating"
  ├→ Document root cause
  └→ Add root cause analysis
  ↓
Create Corrective Actions
  ├→ CAPA #1: Supplier action
  ├→ CAPA #2: Process update
  └→ Set due dates
  ↓
Status → "Awaiting Supplier"
  ↓
Monitor CAPA Completion
  ├→ Supplier completes actions
  ├→ Mark CAPAs as complete
  └→ Verify effectiveness
  ↓
All CAPAs Complete
  ↓
Change Status → "Resolved"
  ↓
Close Complaint
  ├→ Add closure notes
  ├→ Rate effectiveness (1-5)
  └→ Confirm closure
  ↓
Status → "Closed"
  ↓
[Notification] All parties notified
  ↓
End
```

**UI Flow Details:**

**Registration:**

- Form validation prevents submission without required fields
- Severity auto-calculates due date
- File upload shows progress for large files

**Investigation:**

- Timeline shows all status changes
- Internal notes vs. supplier communication tabs
- Root cause modal with template selection

**CAPA Tracking:**

- Each CAPA is a card with status badge
- Due date countdown prominently displayed
- Cannot mark resolved until all CAPAs complete

**Closure:**

- Final modal requires verification
- Effectiveness rating impacts supplier score
- Closed complaints are locked (read-only)

