## Appendix F: Performance Checklist

### Image Optimization

- [ ] Use Next.js Image component for automatic optimization
- [ ] Serve images in WebP format with fallbacks
- [ ] Lazy load images below the fold
- [ ] Use appropriate image sizes (srcset)
- [ ] Compress all images (TinyPNG, ImageOptim)

### Code Splitting

- [ ] Dynamic imports for heavy components
- [ ] Route-based code splitting
- [ ] Lazy load charts only when visible
- [ ] Split vendor bundles

### Caching Strategy

- [ ] Cache API responses (React Query)
- [ ] Cache static assets (Service Worker)
- [ ] Use stale-while-revalidate for non-critical data
- [ ] Implement optimistic updates

### Bundle Size

- [ ] Keep main bundle < 200KB gzipped
- [ ] Use tree-shaking for unused code
- [ ] Analyze bundle with webpack-bundle-analyzer
- [ ] Remove unused dependencies

